<ul>
<li>It will prompt you to select your Excel file.</li>
<li>It will process the data, fit the model, and generate all outputs automatically.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>How to use:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Copy the entire script</strong> above.</li>
<li><strong>Paste it into your R script editor</strong> (such as RStudio or the base R GUI).</li>
<li><strong>Run the script</strong> (you can source the file, or run line by line).</li>
</ol>
<p>If you want to save it as a file, you can do this:</p>
