<p><strong>How to fix:</strong><br>
You can either:</p>
<ul>
<li>Change the column name to a simple one (like <code node="[object Object]">Predicted_VIABILITY</code>), or</li>
<li>Use backticks (`<code node="[object Object]">column name with space</code>`) in <code node="[object Object]">aes()</code>, but this only works in some ggplot2 versions and can be fragile.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Recommended fix:</strong><br>
