<hr>
<h2><strong>How to Process Multiple Sheets at Once</strong></h2>
<h3><strong>General Workflow</strong></h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Read the list of sheet names</strong> from the Excel file.</li>
<li><strong>Loop over each sheet</strong>, applying the analysis script to each.</li>
<li><strong>Save outputs</strong> for each sheet (e.g., add results as new sheets in the output Excel, or save individual result files per sheet).</li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3><strong>Example: Batch Analysis Script Skeleton</strong></h3>
<p>Here’s how you’d modify your script to analyze all sheets in the selected Excel file:</p>
