<h3><strong>Best Practices</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Encapsulate your analysis</strong> for a single sheet in a function (e.g., <code node="[object Object]">analyse_plate()</code>), so you can call it for every sheet easily.</li>
<li>Handle errors gracefully—if one sheet is missing key rows, skip and continue.</li>
<li>You can name output sheets after the original sheet names for clarity.</li>
</ul>
