<p>But for dose–response analysis, <strong>the smooth fitted model is preferred</strong>, not just connecting points.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3>2. <strong>Why are the predicted viabilities (from the model) and the ones used for plotting not in percent?</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>What’s happening:</strong></p>
