<h2><strong>Summary of Best Practices</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Input data:</strong> Keep in percent, as is.</li>
<li><strong>No scaling:</strong> Don’t multiply/divide by 100 in code.</li>
<li><strong>Predicted values:</strong> Will match input scale (percent).</li>
<li><strong>Plot:</strong> Add <code node="[object Object]">geom_line()</code> to connect your points if desired.</li>
</ul>
