<h3><strong>How it works:</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Experimental points</strong>: plotted as dots + connected by a dotted line for visual clarity.</li>
<li><strong>Fitted curve</strong>: smooth LL.4 model overlay.</li>
<li><strong>All values in percent</strong>: no conversion needed.</li>
<li><strong>Output</strong>: Excel file with all data and embedded plots, plus separate PNGs, for each file you select.</li>
