	C14.4974,19.3114,14.4848,20.1128,14.4848,20.4914z"></path></svg></div></div></div></div><div class="ChatMessage-module__content--sWQll"><div class="js-snippet-clipboard-copy-unpositioned ChatMessage-module__messageArea--gxJTG"><h3 class="sr-only">Copilot said: If **no pop-up is displayed** when you</h3><div class="markdown-body MarkdownRenderer-module__container--dNKcF MarkdownViewer-module__markdownOverrides--xtpOl" data-copilot-markdown="true" style="--MarkdownRenderer_streaming-fade-duration: 750ms;"><p>If <strong>no pop-up is displayed</strong> when you run a script using <code node="[object Object]">tcltk::tk_choose.files()</code> or <code node="[object Object]">tcltk::tk_choose.dir()</code>, it usually means one of the following:</p>
<hr>
<h3><strong>1. R is Running in a Non-GUI Environment</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>RStudio Server</strong>, <strong>R in terminal/console only</strong>, or some <strong>remote desktop</strong> sessions <strong>cannot show GUI pop-ups</strong>.</li>
<li>Only RGui (Windows), RStudio Desktop, or other GUI-enabled R environments can display file/folder dialogs.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3><strong>2. Tcl/Tk is Not Properly Installed</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>On some systems, the <code node="[object Object]">tcltk</code> package is not installed or cannot find the underlying Tcl/Tk libraries.</li>
<li>Try this in your R console:
<figure class="CodeBlock-module__container--QRI4L CodeBlock-module__immersive--D8NjT" aria-labelledby=":rrc:"><div class="CodeBlock-module__header--K8Zrp"><span class="LanguageDot-module__languageDot--O6n2z" style="background-color: rgb(25, 140, 231);"></span><span id=":rrc:" class="CodeBlock-module__languageName--fxI6n">R</span><button data-component="IconButton" type="button" class="prc-Button-ButtonBase-c50BI prc-Button-IconButton-szpyj" data-loading="false" data-no-visuals="true" data-size="medium" data-variant="invisible" aria-describedby=":rre:-loading-announcement" aria-labelledby=":rrd:"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 13h3M1 3h14"></path><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 7.25a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h11.5a1.75 1.75 0 1 1 0 3.5H9.536v-.464a.679.679 0 0 0-1.086-.543l-1.619 1.214a.68.68 0 0 0 0 1.086l1.619 1.214a.679.679 0 0 0 1.086-.543v-.464H12.5a3.25 3.25 0 0 0 0-6.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></button><span class="prc-TooltipV2-Tooltip-cYMVY" data-direction="s" aria-hidden="true" id=":rrd:" popover="auto">Wrap</span></div><div class="CodeBlock-module__copyContainer--jLoHL"><div class="CodeBlock-module__copyContent--BH7EX"><button data-component="IconButton" type="button" class="prc-Button-ButtonBase-c50BI CodeBlock-module__copyButton--eyFr8 prc-Button-IconButton-szpyj" data-loading="false" data-no-visuals="true" data-size="medium" data-variant="invisible" aria-describedby=":rrh:-loading-announcement" aria-labelledby=":rrf:"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="octicon octicon-copy" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" display="inline-block" overflow="visible" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;"><path d="M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.5 0v1.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 16h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 14.25Z"></path><path d="M5 1.75C5 .784 5.784 0 6.75 0h7.5C15.216 0 16 .784 16 1.75v7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 14.25 11h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 5 9.25Zm1.75-.25a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25Z"></path></svg></button><span class="CopyToClipboardButton-module__tooltip--HDUYz prc-TooltipV2-Tooltip-cYMVY" data-direction="s" aria-label="Copy code" aria-hidden="true" id=":rrf:" popover="auto">Copy code</span></div></div><div class="CodeBlock-module__codeContainer--snQei"><pre class="CodeBlock-module__code--gyjSL" tabindex="0"><code class="">capabilities<span class="hljs-punctuation" node="[object Object]">(</span><span class="hljs-string" node="[object Object]">"tcltk"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation" node="[object Object]">)</span>
</code></pre></div></figure>
If it returns <code node="[object Object]">FALSE</code>, your R installation cannot use Tcl/Tk GUIs.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3><strong>3. RStudio Desktop: Pop-up Hidden or Behind Other Windows</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Sometimes the dialog is open but hidden behind other windows. Try minimizing or moving windows to check.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2><strong>How to Fix</strong></h2>
<h3><strong>A. Use RStudio Desktop or RGui</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Make sure you’re running your script in <strong>RStudio Desktop</strong> (not RStudio Server/web), or in the base <strong>RGui</strong> on Windows.</li>
</ul>
<h3><strong>B. Check Tcl/Tk Installation</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Windows: Usually comes with R, but you can reinstall R if needed.</li>
<li>Mac: Install XQuartz if missing.</li>
<li>Linux: Install Tcl/Tk libraries (e.g., <code node="[object Object]">sudo apt-get install tcl tk</code>).</li>
</ul>
<h3><strong>C. Alternative: Use File Path Input Instead</strong></h3>
<p>If you still can't get pop-ups, you can <strong>manually specify the folder</strong>:</p>
