<h2><strong>Instructions</strong></h2>
<ol>
<li><strong>Save as:</strong> <code node="[object Object]">app.R</code></li>
<li><strong>Install required R packages</strong> if you don’t have them (<code node="[object Object]">shiny</code>, <code node="[object Object]">readxl</code>, <code node="[object Object]">openxlsx</code>, <code node="[object Object]">drc</code>, <code node="[object Object]">ggplot2</code>, <code node="[object Object]">dplyr</code>, <code node="[object Object]">shinyFiles</code>, <code node="[object Object]">zip</code>)</li>
<li><strong>Run in RStudio:</strong> Click "Run App" or use <code node="[object Object]">shiny::runApp("app.R")</code></li>
<li><strong>Workflow:</strong>
<ul>
<li>Upload Excel files (multiple allowed)</li>
<li>Choose output folder</li>
<li>Adjust outlier threshold if desired</li>
<li>Click "Run Analysis"</li>
<li>See plots instantly in browser (outliers in red)</li>
<li>Download Excel reports for all files (with PNGs in your chosen folder)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
