<hr>
<h2><strong>1. Open RStudio</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Open RStudio on your computer.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2><strong>2. Create a New Script File</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Go to <strong>File &gt; New File &gt; R Script</strong>.</li>
<li>Copy the entire Shiny app code I provided above.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2><strong>3. Save the Script as <code node="[object Object]">app.R</code></strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>Go to <strong>File &gt; Save As</strong>.</li>
<li>Name the file <strong><code node="[object Object]">app.R</code></strong>.</li>
<li>Choose a folder where you want to keep this app.</li>
<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2><strong>4. (Optional) Create a Project Folder</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>You can create a dedicated folder (e.g., <code node="[object Object]">CytotoxicityShinyApp</code>) and save <code node="[object Object]">app.R</code> inside for better organization.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2><strong>5. Run the App</strong></h2>
<ul>
<li>In RStudio, open <code node="[object Object]">app.R</code>.</li>
<li>Click the <strong>"Run App"</strong> button (usually at the top-right of the script editor).</li>
<li>Or, in the R console, type:
<figure class="CodeBlock-module__container--QRI4L CodeBlock-module__immersive--D8NjT" aria-labelledby=":r1ce:"><div class="CodeBlock-module__header--K8Zrp"><span class="LanguageDot-module__languageDot--O6n2z" style="background-color: rgb(25, 140, 231);"></span><span id=":r1ce:" class="CodeBlock-module__languageName--fxI6n">R</span><button data-component="IconButton" type="button" class="prc-Button-ButtonBase-c50BI prc-Button-IconButton-szpyj" data-loading="false" data-no-visuals="true" data-size="medium" data-variant="invisible" aria-describedby=":r1cg:-loading-announcement" aria-labelledby=":r1cf:"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M1 13h3M1 3h14"></path><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 7.25a.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5h11.5a1.75 1.75 0 1 1 0 3.5H9.536v-.464a.679.679 0 0 0-1.086-.543l-1.619 1.214a.68.68 0 0 0 0 1.086l1.619 1.214a.679.679 0 0 0 1.086-.543v-.464H12.5a3.25 3.25 0 0 0 0-6.5z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></button><span class="prc-TooltipV2-Tooltip-cYMVY" data-direction="s" aria-hidden="true" id=":r1cf:" popover="auto">Wrap</span></div><div class="CodeBlock-module__copyContainer--jLoHL"><div class="CodeBlock-module__copyContent--BH7EX"><button data-component="IconButton" type="button" class="prc-Button-ButtonBase-c50BI CodeBlock-module__copyButton--eyFr8 prc-Button-IconButton-szpyj" data-loading="false" data-no-visuals="true" data-size="medium" data-variant="invisible" aria-describedby=":r1cj:-loading-announcement" aria-labelledby=":r1ch:"><svg aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="octicon octicon-copy" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" display="inline-block" overflow="visible" style="vertical-align: text-bottom;"><path d="M0 6.75C0 5.784.784 5 1.75 5h1.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.5h-1.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v7.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25